These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, bird
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, aconite, tulip
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
House: modern, tower, townhouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, december, april
3 different games are played: billiard, whist, poker
 1. the person playing billiard is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person playing poker is the mechanic##1
 3. the owner of the bird is between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the lizard##2
 4. the tower house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the designer is the person who growstulip##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the left of the modern house##1
 9. the person playing billiard is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Pet      | lizard    | bird   | snake           |
| Flower          | aconite       | tulip    | begonia         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| House   | tower        | townhouse    | modern       |
| Birthday   | december     | september  | april       |
| Game         | billiard     | whist | poker |

