.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, traveling, collecting
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, pilot, photographer
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, rose
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, car
3 different games are played: domino, poker, backgammon
 1. the person driving the car is the person who growsdaisy##1
 2. the person driving the car is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person playing domino is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the dressmaker##1
 7. the pilot is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the photographer##1
10. the person driving the car is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Hobby   | chess  | collecting  | traveling     |
| Job   | photographer       | pilot      | dressmaker         |
| Flower   | rose      | daisy   | poppy    |
| Transport           | boat        | car      | snowmobile         |
| Game         | poker | domino  | backgammon |

