3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the bolivar-smoker is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person who growsiris is the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the davidoff-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is between the person who growstulip and the person driving the taxi##2
 8. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
11. the person who growstulip is the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Cigar          | davidoff      | bolivar      | baccarat      |
