 2. the person traveling to liverpool is the malaysian##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person driving the motorbike and the person traveling to liverpool##2
 6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes grey##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
