 6. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching western movies and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person eating strawberry and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 8. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the engineer is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
