There 3 different types of food: artichoke, corn, orange
City: edinburgh, boston, miami
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, pall-mall, oliveros
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, blue, fuchsia
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, dressmaker, mechanic
 1. the person who likes fuchsia is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating corn is in the middle##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 4. the person traveling to miami is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the dancer is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the mechanic is between the person eating artichoke and the montecristo-smoker##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the dancer##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the dancer is the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food      | artichoke | corn      | orange      |
| City         | edinburgh     | boston     | miami  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | oliveros     | montecristo |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Color         | emerald    | fuchsia | blue   |
| Job     | dressmaker        | mechanic        | dancer   |

