.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, brazilian, chinese
3 different games are played: domino, chess, poker
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, mexicansy, september
City: hannover, liverpool, rome
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, marigold
1. the brazilian is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who's birthday is in january and the manager##2
5. the person playing poker is between the musician and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person playing poker##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the brazilian##1
8. the person who growslily is on the left of the chinese##1
9. the person who's birthday is in mexicansy is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Nationality      | mexican      | brazilian      | chinese       |
| Game          | chess      | poker    | domino   |
