There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, lavender, coral
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, doctor, chef
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, blend, old-henry
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the chef is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who likes light-blue##2
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is the chef##1
9. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
