.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, whist
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, red, mauve
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, filmmaking
City: paris, boston, marseilles
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, r&b, hip-hop
1. the person drinking milk is the person playing whist##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person who likes emerald is between the person drinking tea and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the person who likes red is the person playing mah-jongg##1
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
9. the french is between the person playing mah-jongg and the fan of salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Game          | mah-jongg   | whist   | go  |
| Color           | red  | emerald | mauve    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Hobby           | filmmaking     | magic-tricks        | gardening |
| City         | boston | paris   | marseilles  |
| Music-Genre     | r&b    | hip-hop     | salsa      |

 